インタフェースの使用
org.interledger.InterledgerPacket.Handler

  • InterledgerPacket.Handlerを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger
    The main package for top-level Interledger objects.
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.

    • org.interledgerでのInterledgerPacket.Handlerの使用

      InterledgerPacket.Handlerを実装しているorg.interledgerのクラス 
      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      static class  InterledgerPacket.Handler.AbstractHandler<R>
      A handler for allowing callers to specify logic based upon an unknown result type.
      static class  InterledgerPacket.Handler.AbstractHandler.HelperHandler<R>
      A utility class that provides default implementations of InterledgerPacket.Handler.AbstractHandler so that a caller is only forced to implement the handlers that are of interest.

    • org.interledger.codecsでのInterledgerPacket.Handlerの使用

      InterledgerPacket.Handler型のパラメータを持つorg.interledger.codecsのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      <R> R CodecContext.readAndHandle(InputStream inputStream, InterledgerPacket.Handler<R> packetHandler)
      Read an object from inputStream according to the rules defined in the context, handle any concrete logic inside of packetHandler, and return a result.
